# ===== Dependencies (dibuat otomatis saat `docker compose build`) =====
**/node_modules/
**/vendor/

# ===== Build output =====
**/target/
*.jar
*.class

# ===== Python cache =====
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/venv/

# ===== Logs =====
*.log
**/storage/logs/*.log

# ===== OS / IDE =====
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.iml

# Catatan:
# - laravel-service/.env SENGAJA tetap ikut (berisi APP_KEY) agar build Laravel jalan.
# - File .sqlite dibuat otomatis saat container start (migrate), jadi tidak perlu di-commit.
